<br>
In this setup , Id see no real problem with warders/necro pets being on par with our air pet. IE- very good middle of the road pets, decent at both tanking and doing damage.  Honestly, I cant see any reason for beastlords/necros to have completely worse pets then mages in all areas.  <br>
<br>
